Gravelord is a University Project made in Unity3D. It's a rougue like game developed in 1 month. 
The player has to defeat waves of enemies, each of them provides him HP bubbles and some EXP for Leveling up, 
  sometimes a LV up blue bubblew can be dropped.
Level up options consists on HP up, Speed up, Damage up and attack speed up.

Folders contain the code in C#.
The 3 Zip files have the exe built in them.
